message.content: cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SI. The paper discusses the development of a question-answering system using product reviews, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. This falls under the scope of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
